Author: TheAllMightiest
Text: Ngl I lost weight and my engagement ring keeps nearly slipping off my finger in the shower, and I've gone down about half a ring size. Which is not a side effect I wanted!!!

Author: BabyBaphomet_
Text: This is such a mood!!! I'm underweight and my ring size is still 8. It was 9 before at a healthy BMI, but...I want size 4 or 5 fingers so bad.
